        <section name="Introduction">
            <p>Force Field X is a group of open source (GPL v. 3), platform independent
               (Java Runtime Environment) modules for molecular biophysics.
               Key features include:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Polarizable AMOEBA force fields</li>
                <li>Particle-mesh Ewald electrostatics</li>
                <li>X-ray crystallography refinement</li>
                <li>Methods for structure based drug design</li>
            </ul>
